---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Tambak Bayan GO-WEB - Koleksi Mural" description="Jelajahi berbagai karya mural di Tambak Bayan.">
  <style>
    .interior-card-wrap {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .interior-card-wrap::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      background: #5c2908;
      transform: rotate(-4deg) translate(6px, 8px);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .interior-card-wrap::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      background: #3b1505;
      opacity: 0.5;
      transform: rotate(-7deg) translate(12px, 14px);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .interior-card-wrap img {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      border: 2.5px solid rgba(92, 41, 8, 0.55);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      display: block;
      transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
    }
    .mural-watermark {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      padding-top: 0.5rem;
    }
    .mural-watermark .wm-row {
      display: block;
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #7c3a10;
      opacity: 0.22;
      font-size: clamp(14px, 2.8vw, 38px);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .mural-watermark .wm-row { font-size: clamp(11px, 4vw, 22px); }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <section class="w-full overflow-hidden" aria-label="Hero Mural">
    <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/3] sm:aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[21/9]">
      <img src="/assets/koleksi-mural/koleksi-mural-home.webp" alt="Mural bertuliskan WELCOME TO TAMBAK BAYAN"
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2-column content -->
  <section class="w-full overflow-hidden" aria-label="Konten Koleksi Mural"
    style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #EEBB3B 0%, #d6851a 38%, #B92E2B 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-14 lg:gap-20">
        <div class="w-full md:w-[42%] flex-shrink-0 px-4 md:px-0">
          <div class="interior-card-wrap max-w-[380px] mx-auto md:mx-0">
            <img src="/assets/koleksi-mural/Koleksi-Mural-2.webp" alt="Interior Tambak Bayan dengan lampion" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-[58%] relative min-h-[260px]">
          <div class="mural-watermark">
            <span class="wm-row">MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN</span>
            <span class="wm-row">MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN</span>
            <span class="wm-row">MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN</span>
            <span class="wm-row">MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN</span>
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 py-2">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-white text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.4rem] leading-snug mb-5 drop-shadow-sm tracking-wide">
              KOLEKSI MURAL TAMBAK BAYAN
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white text-base sm:text-[1.05rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
              Di sini, kamu bisa menjelajahi berbagai karya mural yang tidak hanya indah dilihat, tapi juga penuh dengan makna.
            </p>
            <p class="text-white text-base sm:text-[1.05rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-relaxed mb-9 text-justify hyphens-auto">
              Yuk, pilih kategori yang kamu suka dan temukan cerita unik di balik setiap goresan seni!
            </p>
            <a href="/detail-koleksi-mural/"
              class="inline-block px-6 py-3 sm:px-8 sm:py-3.5 rounded-full border-2 border-white/90 bg-white/10 text-white font-semibold text-sm sm:text-base tracking-wide backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-white hover:text-[#B92E2B] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#B92E2B] transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl">
              Jelajah Cerita di Balik Mural Tambak Bayan
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
